Start 
Loading screen loads
Title screen opens
Ask the user if they want to use the tax calculator or currency convertor
If press currency convertor will open another window called currency convertor 
User selects within the dropdown menu
User will type into the amount input
User presses convert when done
User can go to the tax calculator or exit application
If tax calculator is pressed, then open the tax calculator window 
User inputs an amount and tax is calculated depending on what is being taxed
The final amount is shown and the user can calculate the final price of an item many items
The user can then exit the application 
